       Coverage_Stg.ParentId,
       Coverage_Stg.Id,

       Coverage_Stg.FinalPremiumAmt,
       Coverage_Stg.RatingInd

where cmmcontainer = 'Policy'

object.customQuery:
select 
    coverage.coveragekey as coveragekey,
    coverage.coverageid as coverageid,
    coverage.coveragehashkey as coveragehashkey,
    coverage.policykey as policykey
from 
    dbo.coverage coverage
inner join 
    dbo.coverage_stg cs 
on 
    cs.id= coverage.coverageid
where 
    coverage.roweffenddt = '9999-12-31' --

SELECT Risk.SystemId as SystemId, 
Risk.Id as Id 
FROM Risk
where CMMContainer = 'Policy'

SELECT  min(Risk.UnderlyingRiskId) AS UnderlyingRiskId,  Risk.SystemId AS SystemId,  Risk.ParentId AS ParentId FROM Risk
WHERE CMMContainer = 'Policy'
and UnderlyingRiskId is not null
group by Risk.Systemid, Risk.ParentId

Risk.SystemId as SystemId, 
Risk.ParentId as ParentId 
FROM Risk
WHERE CMMContainer = 'Policy'
group by Risk.Systemid, Risk.ParentId

object.name: PolicyStats
object.customQuery:
select distinct ps.startdt as StartDt, 
ps.enddt as EndDt, 
ps.policyref as PolicyRef, 
ps.coveragecd as CoverageCd
from
policystats ps
join
(
select distinct policyref, coveragecd, 
min(case when bookdt > effectivedt then bookdt else effectivedt end) as checkdt
from policystats
group by policyref, coveragecd
) sub
on ps.policyref = sub.policyref
and ps.coveragecd = sub.coveragecd
and (ps.bookdt = sub.checkdt or ps.effectivedt = sub.checkdt)
order by policyref, CoverageCd ##
